<p>Thrill-seeker or gentle meandering - when to hit the slopes? <strong>- </strong>We are here to ensure that on your next ski holiday, you can enjoy that breath of fresh air, get your heart racing and your body soaring whilst you make the most of the great outdoors and all that alpine-life has to offer. </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Best months to ski</h2>
<p>With a fantastic long ski season across Europe and Canada, there are so many opportunities to take a great ski or snowboard holiday. To help you decide when to go, we have put together some highlights per month:</p>
